'''Daniele Battaglia''' (born 21 July 1981) is an Italian [[singer]] and television personality.<ref name="Battaglia1">{{cite web|url=https://it.tv.yahoo.com/blog/tv-star/daniele-battaglia-basta-paragonarmi-francesco-facchinetti-110647996.html |title=Daniele Battaglia: "Basta paragonarmi a Francesco Facchinetti" |publisher=It.tv |date= |accessdate=25 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426202253/https://it.tv.yahoo.com/blog/tv-star/daniele-battaglia-basta-paragonarmi-francesco-facchinetti-110647996.html |archivedate=April 26, 2014 }}</ref> In 2011 Battaglia participated in and won the seventh season of the [[RAI 2]] reality show ''[[L'isola dei famosi]]''.<ref name="Battaglia1"/><ref name="Battaglia2">{{cite web|url= http://societa.panorama.it/televisione/L-Isola-dei-Famosi-7-vince-Daniele-Battaglia-ma-la-trasmissione-non-decolla|title= L'Isola dei Famosi 7: vince Daniele Battaglia, ma la trasmissione non decolla|publisher=Panorama|date=|accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref>

He is the son of the musician [[Dodi Battaglia]].

